title: Steve Hackett - Voyage of the Acolyte (2005 Remaster) (m4a)
description:
2005 remaster of Steve Hackett's debut solo album, Voyage of the Acolyte (m4a):

1. Ace of Wands
2. Hands of the Priestess, Pt. 1
3. A Tower Struck Down
4. Hands of the Priestess, Pt. 2
5. The Hermit
6. Star of Sirius
7. The Lovers
8. Shadow of the Hierophant
9. Ace of Wands (Live At The Theatre Royal, Drury Lane)
10. Shadow of the Hierophant (Extended playout version)

Enjoy!
